OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1783820902
OL,3,CTrump agrees to talks with Iran after
OL,4,Clatest strikes but says ceasefire
OL,5,C'over'
OL,7,FDonald Trump has said the US has
OL,8,Fagreed to continue talks with Iran
OL,9,Fafter recent clashes but stressed in
OL,10,F"no uncertain terms" that the
OL,11,Fceasefire was over.
OL,13,FThe US president gave the update in a
OL,14,Fpost on his Truth Social platform,
OL,15,Fhaving earlier in the week branded the
OL,16,FTehran leadership "scum" and said it
OL,17,Fwas "a waste of time" dealing with the
OL,18,Fregime.
