PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1783820902
OL,3,CTrump agrees to talks with Iran after
OL,4,Clatest strikes but says ceasefire
OL,5,C'over'
OL,7,FIt follows recent exchanges of fire
OL,8,Fbetween the two sides over the
OL,9,Fstrategic Strait of Hormuz waterway,
OL,10,Fwhich had tested the fragile truce.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, no-one has yet claimed
OL,13,Fresponsibility for airstrikes that hit
OL,14,FIran after the US said it had
OL,15,Fconcluded its attacks.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
