PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1783820902
OL,3,CTrump agrees to talks with Iran after
OL,4,Clatest strikes but says ceasefire
OL,5,C'over'
OL,7,FTrump said: "The Islamic Republic of
OL,8,FIran has asked us to continue 'talks'.
OL,10,F"We have agreed to do so, but the
OL,11,FUnited States has stated to them, in
OL,12,Fno uncertain terms, that the Cease
OL,13,FFire is OVER!"
OL,15,FThe renewed hostilities broke out on
OL,16,FTuesday after Iran targeted three
OL,17,Ftankers in the strait, which has
OL,18,Fremained a flashpoint.
OL,26,@oD@MOUrD@AOUuD@NO]
