PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1783820902
OL,3,CTrump agrees to talks with Iran after
OL,4,Clatest strikes but says ceasefire
OL,5,C'over'
OL,7,FThe trading of strikes has again
OL,8,Fcaused severe disruption to maritime
OL,9,Ftraffic in the critical sea route as
OL,10,Fwell as casting doubt on securing a
OL,11,Fpermanent end to the conflict,
OL,12,Flaunched by the US and Israel on
OL,13,FFebruary 28.
OL,15,FTrump has also suggested the US could
OL,16,Freimpose its blockade of Iranian
OL,17,Fports, having already pulled Tehran's
OL,18,Flicence to sell oil.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
