PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1783820902
OL,3,CTrump agrees to talks with Iran after
OL,4,Clatest strikes but says ceasefire
OL,5,C'over'
OL,7,FOn Friday, the US Treasury moved to
OL,8,Fcrack down on a key financier to the
OL,9,FTehran regime, Dubai-based banker and
OL,10,Fbusinessman Ali Ansari, previously
OL,11,Fsanctioned by Britain for his role in
OL,12,Ffinancially supporting the activities
OL,13,Fof Iran's Islamic Revolutionary Guard
OL,14,FCorps (IRGC).
OL,16,FPrior to the latest flare-up,
OL,17,Fnegotiations between the two sides had
OL,18,Fbeen due to restart following the
OL,19,Fburial of Iran's late supreme leader
OL,20,FAyatollah Ali Khamenei, who was killed
OL,21,Fon the first day of the conflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
