PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1783820902
OL,3,CTrump agrees to talks with Iran after
OL,4,Clatest strikes but says ceasefire
OL,5,C'over'
OL,7,FEnding Tehran's stranglehold on the
OL,8,Fstrait, which disrupted global oil and
OL,9,Fgas supplies and drove up fuel and
OL,10,Ffood prices, had been a key demand in
OL,11,Fprevious negotiations.
OL,13,FHowever, the initial deal reached
OL,14,Fbetween the US and Iran only provides
OL,15,Ffor safe, toll-free passage of the
OL,16,Fwaterway for 60 days, pending the
OL,17,Foutcome of a final agreement on
OL,18,FTehran's disputed nuclear plans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
