FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1783820902
OL,3,CTrump agrees to talks with Iran after
OL,4,Clatest strikes but says ceasefire
OL,5,C'over'
OL,7,FThe pact also leaves it to Iran and
OL,8,FOman, in conjunction with other Gulf
OL,9,Fstates, to "define the future
OL,10,Fadministration and maritime services
OL,11,Fin the Strait of Hormuz".
OL,13,FIn the meantime, Iran has continued to
OL,14,Ftry to exert leverage over the
OL,15,Fchannel, including demanding ships
OL,16,Fseek permission to transit and raising
OL,17,Fthe spectre of future charges.
OL,26,@qD@LOUsD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
