PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1783820902
OL,3,CTrump agrees to talks with Iran after
OL,4,Clatest strikes but says ceasefire
OL,5,C'over'
OL,7,FThe US military has sought to counter
OL,8,Fclaims by Iran that it controls the
OL,9,Fsea route and that transit is only
OL,10,Fpermitted through its approved
OL,11,Fdesignated routes.
OL,13,FNevertheless, shipping using the
OL,14,Fchannel has plummeted following the
OL,15,Frecent fighting, with traffic already
OL,16,Fwell down compared to before the war.
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
